description:
Retrieve 1 friendly piece. Retrieving pieces of different gun types has different effects.
HG: Gain 1 additional movement die for 1 turn;
RF: Gain a <a press=280294>devastation</a>-related Item Card;
SMG: All pieces gain 2 shield points;
AR: Gain an <a press=280121>enhancement</a>-related Item Card.
